{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover an explosive mix of platformer, roguelite, and survivor! Transform your world, enhance your character, use your items, and battle hordes of enemies and formidable bosses\u2014find your way to victory! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy a game feel based on intuitive, physics-driven mechanics! Explore Under Death to understand its workings and secrets, battle powerful demons with various abilities, and survive attacks from all tormented souls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123780/extras/Under_Death_1.gif?t=1729114399\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your death will be far from restful: you're trapped in Under Death, a world where lost souls traverse time. It's a world with its own rules, where the law of the strongest prevails. But an external force has granted you a mysterious power: you can free souls that will help you escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123780/extras/Under_Death_2.gif?t=1729114399\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>With each game, you will be able to enhance your interactions with this world to find new ways to play!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123780/extras/Under_Death_3.gif?t=1729114399\" /><strong>Your action-gaming skills will be put to the test with very fluid and instinctive gameplay. But don't overlook the strategy for evolving your character.</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123780/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729114399","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123780/page.bg.jpg?t=1729114399","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com